description: This file defines a React functional component for managing and displaying a list of connectors, including functionalities for fetching, deleting, and creating connectors. It utilizes hooks like useState, useEffect, and useCallback, and integrates with external API functions and UI components.

methods.name: load
methods.description: Fetches the list of connectors from API and updates state.

methods.name: remove
methods.description: Deletes a specific connector by ID after user confirmation and reloads the list.

methods.name: submit
methods.description: Handles creating a new connector and updates the UI accordingly.
